{"tid":882231,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"C905領軍 Sony Ericsson 十月推出5款強機","createTime":"2018-10-30T04:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T17:00:59.000Z","uid":6752,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2788a1a2b77e9d85c694186b2bffcf526fd004e1","tid":882231,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:23:06.000Z","msg":"七週年紀念推新機<br />\n<br />\nSE 在邁入七週年的紀念日之際，舉辦了一場相當特別的新機發表會，不僅請來了名模群來站台，也將記者會上發表的五款新機化身為棒球選手，由名主播蔡明里播報球賽實況，敘述五支手機的強大功能，而這五支即將推出的新機分別是W595、W902、T700、X1 及 C902，相當難得的在同一場記者會同時集結 SE 熱賣的 Walkman 音樂系列、時尚系列、PDA系列、Cyber-Shot 系列，另外也一併推出新的藍牙周邊商品 MBS-400、MPS-100、HBH-PV715。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://defzd6kpftjvs.cloudfront.net/img_park/7659/IMG_4954.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdefzd6kpftjvs.cloudfront.net%2Fimg_park%2F7659%2FIMG_4954.jpg&h=5b3d599e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ W595 及 W902 是 Walkman 系列新的生力軍，其中 W902 是 Walkman 系列中第一支支援五百萬畫素自動對焦的手機。W902 預計推出幕色黑、酒紅雙色，建議售價為 17,500 元；W595 預計有灰、白、藍三色，預計 10 月初上市，但售價未定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://defzd6kpftjvs.cloudfront.net/img_park/7659/IMG_4974.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdefzd6kpftjvs.cloudfront.net%2Fimg_park%2F7659%2FIMG_4974.jpg&h=75cb7118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ T700 仿自 T610i 的時尚造型，此次出擊外型更加纖細，要讓消費者簡直好看。一共有銀黑、紅黑、閃亮銀的 T700，建議售價為 8,900 元，這幾天就能買到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://defzd6kpftjvs.cloudfront.net/img_park/7659/IMG_4989.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdefzd6kpftjvs.cloudfront.net%2Fimg_park%2F7659%2FIMG_4989.jpg&h=3177ab18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ C905 是 SE 第一支810 萬畫素 Cyber-shot 手機，也是台灣市場上的第一支。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://defzd6kpftjvs.cloudfront.net/img_park/7659/IMG_5000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdefzd6kpftjvs.cloudfront.net%2Fimg_park%2F7659%2FIMG_5000.jpg&h=a87be621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 沉寂了好久，SE 終於推出 XPERIA X1 ，是 Sony Ericsson 第一款採用 Windows Mobile 6.0 Professional 系統的 PDA 手機，10 月上市的為英文版本，中文版要等到 2009 年第一季才會上市。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">空降機王震撼市場</span><br />\n<br />\nSony Ericsson 在十月份即將推出新一代的 Cyber-Shot 系列 C905，在市面上還依然在讚嘆 500 萬畫素相機的好時，C905 一下子將相機畫素拉高到 800 畫素，相信一定會讓許多手機玩家興奮不已，其實各家廠商都已經有消息傳出 800 萬畫素將會上市，不過大多還是抱持著觀望的態度，而 SE 算是這一波熱潮的領先者，加上自家 Cyber-Shot 的加持，在市場上又要熱銷許久了 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://defzd6kpftjvs.cloudfront.net/img_park/7659/IMG_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdefzd6kpftjvs.cloudfront.net%2Fimg_park%2F7659%2FIMG_1.jpg&h=2325045a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d0431da4fee52d9006c8074d2d3e8e213464968","tid":882231,"uid":166226,"like":0,"dislike":28,"score":-28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:24:14.000Z","msg":"乜撚野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做回帶撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdc75312e911df18ce646916270ec9263a41191","tid":882231,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7d0431da4fee52d9006c8074d2d3e8e213464968","tid":882231,"uid":166226,"like":0,"dislike":28,"score":-28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:24:14.000Z","msg":"乜撚野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做回帶撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"咁都仲要問?<br />\n唔好懶醒喇"},{"pid":"deae6c4a7067a029588effc7e41270b5af40ae1c","tid":882231,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:26:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RYIHRyN-YnE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRYIHRyN-YnE&d=VKt%2BBTUSQjqnA60UG1acky7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=88b0aff4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RYIHRyN-YnE</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc5ef92db3f4ba1d7bcf66fcec43dfb3cfc28c9","tid":882231,"uid":1823,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04